data.description:
Welcome to your new sanctuary. This charming corner lot, 2-story home is a rare find in the prestigious gated community of Country Commons. The living area has many windows for warm morning light that invite you into your backyard to discover a private retreat that will become your favorite spot for relaxation. The inviting deck and arbour create a perfect setting for outdoor dining, entertaining, or simply unwinding with a book while enjoying the shade from the majestic oak trees. A large foyer draws you into the living room with warm fireplace and dining area. The kitchen offers an open bar into the living room. Upstairs, you'll find the three comfortable bedrooms, including a master suite with an ensuite bathroom and a built in desk for your office space. 
Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the warmth and charm of this wonderful property. Your new beginning awaits!
Owner is willing to discuss improvement concessions or buydown points.
